# Hospital Analysis Dashboard â€“ Power BI

## 1. Project Overview

This project is a comprehensive **Hospital Analysis Dashboard built using Power BI** that provides an integrated view of **patients, doctors, hospital operations, and financial performance**.  
It is designed to support **hospital administrators, finance teams, and clinical managers** in making data-driven decisions.

The dashboard consists of **five major analytical sections**:
- Overview
- Patient Analysis
- Doctor Analysis
- Hospital Operations
- Finance Analysis

---

## 2. Tools & Technology Used

- Power BI Desktop  
- Excel / CSV Dataset  
- Data Cleaning & DAX Measures  
- Interactive KPIs, Slicers, and Visuals  

---

## 3. Dashboard Pages & Business Insights

---

### 3.1 Overview Dashboard

This page provides a **high-level snapshot of the entire hospital performance**.

**Key KPIs Displayed:**
- Total Patients: 30  
- Total Doctors: 15  
- Staff Count: 20  
- Total Amount: 854K  
- Discharged Percentage: 73.3%  
- Recently Admitted Patients  
- Bed Status (Occupied vs Available)
- Medicine Stock Status
- Charges Breakdown:
  - Surgery Charges
  - Room Charges
  - Test Charges
  - Other Charges
  - Doctor Fees
  - Medicine Charges  

**Business Value:**
- Enables quick executive-level monitoring.
- Identifies patient flow trends and revenue distribution.
- Tracks medicine inventory and appointment schedules.

